<body>
    <h1>T3 - Technical Document</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <h1 local-id=3D"944b808bdd43" id=3D"T3-TechnicalDocument-1.Introduc=
tion">
<style>[data-colorid=3Dbnwvyq8jgl]{color:#97a0af} html[data-color-mode=3Dda=
rk] [data-colorid=3Dbnwvyq8jgl]{color:#505968}[data-colorid=3Dg5vgyrcow2]{c=
olor:#97a0af} html[data-color-mode=3Ddark] [data-colorid=3Dg5vgyrcow2]{colo=
r:#505968}[data-colorid=3Dcxvuk0tsji]{color:#97a0af} html[data-color-mode=
=3Ddark] [data-colorid=3Dcxvuk0tsji]{color:#505968}[data-colorid=3Dmjpyerem=
3m]{color:#97a0af} html[data-color-mode=3Ddark] [data-colorid=3Dmjpyerem3m]=
{color:#505968}[data-colorid=3Dr72wsj9tgx]{color:#97a0af} html[data-color-m=
ode=3Ddark] [data-colorid=3Dr72wsj9tgx]{color:#505968}[data-colorid=3Dlhw49=
qesmz]{color:#97a0af} html[data-color-mode=3Ddark] [data-colorid=3Dlhw49qes=
mz]{color:#505968}</style>1. Introduction</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"373d29e6e079" id=3D"T3-TechnicalDocument-1.1Purpose">1.1 Pu=
rpose</h2>
<p local-id=3D"a261fdbf0ba3">This document describes the implementation of =
a 2-tier application deployment and database backup automation using AWS EC=
2, MySQL, PM2, and Amazon S3.</p>
<p local-id=3D"2baa16c9d87d">This document is intended for:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"a21a944d-af0c-4ae8-99d8-eaef09daa3b7">
<li local-id=3D"7e334159-cb47-4811-b0ca-0e9ab3549333">
<p local-id=3D"3ba68c04c9ad">CTO</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c283f0af-6033-4318-836c-dd99ef158345">
<p local-id=3D"7090c5893f72">Developers</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"53cb873f-8ca4-4d03-a460-2819fdf10daf">
<p local-id=3D"8af45f67473f">DevOps Engineers</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"44165a05-ab54-4539-b8b6-b1801f899dc0">
<p local-id=3D"0fd778a6c78e">Solution Architects</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"72278597-8391-44c4-a193-5be158cbf6b7">
<p local-id=3D"29127b92b6de">Resellers</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"23e3e6f12857">It explains the infrastructure setup, deployme=
nt automation, backup strategy, monitoring approach, and cost consideration=
s.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"ffd6715c-0ef7-4d65-a7ed-8016b23a8460">
<h2 local-id=3D"f6b965696fe6" id=3D"T3-TechnicalDocument-1.2Scope">1.2 Scop=
e</h2>
<p local-id=3D"239839a8f3ce">This document covers:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"59ec93fb-5e9a-483b-8b6e-c8bf9443876c">
<li local-id=3D"2d3fe652-24eb-417e-92dc-ce281bf9b246">
<p local-id=3D"e3fd986f896a">Manual provisioning of EC2 instances</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b1d91f52-1769-4ef9-870f-814fcb6f2782">
<p local-id=3D"bbc6fe1199b9">Deployment automation using <code>deploy.sh</c=
ode></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5c633fd6-4797-41bc-8e96-a236080752bf">
<p local-id=3D"0ec5dca46f3b">Database backup automation using <code>db_back=
up.sh</code></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9aaa0b8e-ea82-4123-b380-62794ccbe57b">
<p local-id=3D"97337b9d756f">Cron-based hourly backups</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8c81c98a-5845-4667-9270-5d6ce6739b4c">
<p local-id=3D"36a0dc7bb1f2">S3 storage integration</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4ef3d1e4-eecc-4909-88a2-f18b490f3194">
<p local-id=3D"8b62088e69de">Basic monitoring using logs and PM2</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"cc5235fe-ea87-4390-b382-e7d5aa011f33">
<p local-id=3D"e24c4d80366e">Route verification of application</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"aa810b1fbd4b">This implementation focuses on a simple but pr=
oduction-like DevOps workflow.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"4baa1349-0bad-4213-9952-2fbc84dfa99c">
<h1 local-id=3D"5a20d680995e" id=3D"T3-TechnicalDocument-2.OverviewofDevOps=
Project">2. Overview of DevOps Project</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"99e8e414c18c" id=3D"T3-TechnicalDocument-2.1Definition">2.1=
 Definition</h2>
<p local-id=3D"e428d750c7a0">A DevOps Project integrates development and op=
erations to:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"870fd76c-cf5d-435c-a4bf-4179de7af8d1">
<li local-id=3D"08f9e9d9-3d8f-49f4-b3a7-5652efadf68f">
<p local-id=3D"416a5620b5ba">Automate deployments</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9f55cc90-c112-4837-813d-25b3b171fa6f">
<p local-id=3D"bb5aa2e30fef">Improve reliability</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"62d36773-02b6-486e-a2ad-0269f60d7e70">
<p local-id=3D"dfcdae652a35">Reduce manual intervention</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a0e35804-65b9-4a09-82fa-b22a572e0f8b">
<p local-id=3D"b9776d69a3e3">Increase deployment speed</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ec738685-aeeb-45c2-a636-5eac0cd5a2d8">
<p local-id=3D"72e1a3d40ffa">Ensure data safety through backups</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"b7843206-1d7e-4ccc-9c5e-3cf46ba52b9e">
<h2 local-id=3D"ee28030fa4e3" id=3D"T3-TechnicalDocument-2.2AWSWell-Archite=
ctedFramework(6Pillars)">2.2 AWS Well-Architected Framework (6 Pillars)</h2=
>
<h3 local-id=3D"6e48e7b7f7c5" id=3D"T3-TechnicalDocument-1.OperationalExcel=
lence">1. Operational Excellence</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"2bfb723e-9ec6-4244-b523-d92d24dd5537">
<li local-id=3D"4d9a3f2e-2fce-4ba4-914f-4697c6035b6c">
<p local-id=3D"6a9b211e42be">Used deploy.sh for repeatable deployment</p></=
li>
<li local-id=3D"483d0799-b2a6-4b36-8133-6442a39c0a69">
<p local-id=3D"f836b46d9c1b">Used logs (deploy.log, db_backup.log)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"48a25f98-5614-4974-8f63-6c75c08286f7">
<p local-id=3D"3ef261f7667d">Used PM2 for process management</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"6384ac2d030b" id=3D"T3-TechnicalDocument-2.Security">2. Sec=
urity</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"28870982-fc39-4dad-99b7-6a6bf5ebe85f">
<li local-id=3D"56b93583-5906-4862-8845-8db6679548ad">
<p local-id=3D"f9c6048c0cf0">Private IP used for DB connection</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"10c9424a-08d0-444a-9039-2d7908387003">
<p local-id=3D"37a14b2d95c8">IAM permissions for S3 access</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"af8b0ea7-8df9-4d19-8d72-5701e385de7d">
<p local-id=3D"b58a09165a46">MySQL authentication plugin updated</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"b0a14a04f02c" id=3D"T3-TechnicalDocument-3.Reliability">3.R=
eliability</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"578a080d-1002-40c0-93de-813c542a9b46">
<li local-id=3D"351a0e8b-2025-4d1a-97a5-19cc0ba8e17f">
<p local-id=3D"0741a57852e8">PM2 auto restarts app</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d4db4441-adf6-4596-81de-773c8c1d2db7">
<p local-id=3D"1b541f24efc3">Hourly automated database backup</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4caff91a-965c-4745-9211-6d6a7326a294">
<p local-id=3D"485a772eab79">Backups stored in S3</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"6a9fb537db40" id=3D"T3-TechnicalDocument-4.PerformanceEffic=
iency">4. Performance Efficiency</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"ccfa3ca6-69b3-4214-a83b-1c369ac975ed">
<li local-id=3D"98c9170a-6605-4e12-b70d-aa1f92d76b65">
<p local-id=3D"9482a023b682">Used t3.micro for lightweight workload</p></li=
>
<li local-id=3D"f5d54662-6250-4219-a52f-1937a11b2c53">
<p local-id=3D"5a072e93949e">Separated app and DB servers</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"ba075e354a53" id=3D"T3-TechnicalDocument-5.CostOptimization=
">5. Cost Optimization</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"3e1c24a4-7bd8-4da6-b43c-af1d3117903c">
<li local-id=3D"bd2bac82-5102-479a-b73b-b9a96b053719">
<p local-id=3D"df83f59dac18">Used minimal EC2 instances</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c4c9e3fb-798a-4ccf-92da-e10467b3e346">
<p local-id=3D"53d2805f05d4">Standard S3 storage class</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b2f7be80-1f35-495c-a8cc-189e70d539b7">
<p local-id=3D"7cb9515598a0">No unnecessary services</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"1cae5ae69787" id=3D"T3-TechnicalDocument-6.Sustainability">=
6. Sustainability</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"20fe47e3-1e27-44a6-ad82-a1b49bf7b6ec">
<li local-id=3D"5c89bcf1-3417-4d47-bb11-cd99487d06c2">
<p local-id=3D"eacc5995f2db">Small instance sizes</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e775d1e6-5bef-4476-a04b-6d3e8450a252">
<p local-id=3D"7de50d3aea02">No over-provisioned resources</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"7d642311-d1cb-47d4-8dd2-12b919742fc7">
<h2 local-id=3D"5ca6e6f67c28" id=3D"T3-TechnicalDocument-2.3Goals&amp;Objec=
tives">2.3 Goals &amp; Objectives</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"ffc3db33-d5cb-420a-a0fb-91d28aa13cd3">
<li local-id=3D"30b18dbd-096e-4c08-92af-caee6a93fbc4">
<p local-id=3D"7e8e68c5fef3">Deploy 2-tier Node.js + MySQL app</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7e4ca16b-7239-406e-8cbe-8f218bfa5cc4">
<p local-id=3D"cedfcee577f8">Automate deployments</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fce67d59-85da-424c-bbc0-9378416e7778">
<p local-id=3D"89029002bfa1">Automate database backups</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4f9d2734-b6fc-427d-8f87-d7fd64a79e39">
<p local-id=3D"3a4c6721d23a">Store backups in S3</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"bfb5e9e7-8d7c-4837-b625-e34352eed09d">
<p local-id=3D"dea60f380f20">Schedule backups every 1 hour</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"13f450c7-f6e9-4749-aefb-4e15ee99f827">
<p local-id=3D"4de3b40458fb">Validate API routes</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"1f28b74c-a730-4d42-b69b-749d1ae9a934">
<h2 local-id=3D"3e46514885e6" id=3D"T3-TechnicalDocument-2.4Constraints&amp=
;Assumptions">2.4 Constraints &amp; Assumptions</h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"4f92035f6325" id=3D"T3-TechnicalDocument-Constraints">Const=
raints</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"42922ddd-6c4d-498b-8ded-538b9540d5de">
<li local-id=3D"80c07585-9dda-44bb-a2dd-a185c4d2bd09">
<p local-id=3D"f9f557effa45">Limited time (5 hours)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"aac067c6-5499-4b68-aecb-f0416f15b405">
<p local-id=3D"0a9b09939b09">Budget (t3.micro only)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f538ebc4-d9bb-42bf-9bb8-d7370ac1ff8d">
<p local-id=3D"819db36f0a63">Manual EC2 provisioning</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"57ea72670c13" id=3D"T3-TechnicalDocument-Assumptions">Assum=
ptions</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"efb2dc3c-6698-4d09-8125-aa36f4db0662">
<li local-id=3D"d1ccdf3e-6b99-4641-a01d-5d48a940abab">
<p local-id=3D"99f30c7c7e6d">AWS CLI configured</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"dafd616d-111a-473a-9c33-e0beb668d581">
<p local-id=3D"87a3ea6de198">IAM permissions granted</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f9af1db3-ba1f-4c3b-9067-70096988a327">
<p local-id=3D"e7559bf25e1d">Node.js and MySQL installed</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"79520a2f-0b3c-486a-85bb-d42fe2ce53a0">
<h1 local-id=3D"9597f810befd" id=3D"T3-TechnicalDocument-3.Architecture&amp=
;Infrastructure">3. Architecture &amp; Infrastructure</h1>
<h3 local-id=3D"2ca94b0d63a8" id=3D"T3-TechnicalDocument-AWSArchitectureDia=
gram">AWS Architecture Diagram</h3>
<p local-id=3D"46f07ae259c2"></p><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wr=
apper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D"c=
onfluence-embedded-image image-center" alt=3D"diagram-export-3-5-2026-12_40=
_49-AM-20260304-191245.png" width=3D"468" loading=3D"lazy" src=3D"5752d5675=
15826e3b5a6f204bfb6797028a8af70d08906b7ff7128b463b1e8ee" data-image-src=3D"=
https://iamops.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1776812138/diagram-e=
xport-3-5-2026-12_40_49-AM-20260304-191245.png?version=3D1&amp;modification=
Date=3D1772651586407&amp;cacheVersion=3D1&amp;api=3Dv2" data-height=3D"402"=
 data-width=3D"986" data-unresolved-comment-count=3D"0" data-linked-resourc=
e-id=3D"1829666839" data-linked-resource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource=
-type=3D"attachment" data-linked-resource-default-alias=3D"diagram-export-3=
-5-2026-12_40_49-AM-20260304-191245.png" data-base-url=3D"https://iamops.at=
lassian.net/wiki" data-linked-resource-content-type=3D"image/png" data-link=
ed-resource-container-id=3D"1776812138" data-linked-resource-container-vers=
ion=3D"4" data-media-id=3D"021c1362-8127-48d2-9ad2-def692db31a6" data-media=
-type=3D"file" height=3D"190"></span>
<p local-id=3D"558083a9ec34"></p>
<h2 local-id=3D"6cf2677e3230" id=3D"T3-TechnicalDocument-3.1InfrastructureO=
verview">3.1 Infrastructure Overview</h2>
<p local-id=3D"90269b84b7c4">Architecture consists of:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"76950d7a-84a3-4c4a-85a2-b507ec0edb0d">
<li local-id=3D"b9f3f422-feec-4964-a6f5-7018e7c35b93">
<p local-id=3D"d8fd8d9efb0c">EC2 Instance 1 =E2=86=92 Application Server</p=
></li>
<li local-id=3D"3912eb53-d1b2-424a-83ed-6f6bdaa9c0cb">
<p local-id=3D"07c457ad4ed2">EC2 Instance 2 =E2=86=92 Database Server</p></=
li>
